author: wn.com
title: White House issues veto threat for Senate military construction bill
text: WASHINGTON (Reuters) - The White House issued a veto threat on Thursday for a Senate appropriations bill for military construction, Veterans Affairs and related agencies, saying the bill would lock in cuts and prevent it from closing the Guantanamo Bay detention facility.
